      "coreDefinition": "The Charter protects fundamental freedoms, democratic rights, mobility rights, legal rights, equality rights, and language rights.",
      "frameworkSteps": [
        "Identify relevant Charter right.",
        "Determine whether state action is involved.",
        "Assess whether right is infringed.",
        "Apply Section 1 analysis if infringement found."
      ],
      "quickExamples": [
